    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This car is in fair condition. The exterior shows several visible scratches, scuffs, and minor dents consistent with regular use over time. The interior has noticeable wear on the seating surfaces, dashboard, and trim, with some areas showing fading or minor damage. The mechanical systems are functional, though the car may benefit from some maintenance or repairs. Overall, it is a usable vehicle that shows its age.",
